casebody.data:
PEOPLE
v.
MCCAW S236618 Supreme Court of California October 19, 2016

Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The People's petition for review is granted. Further action in this matter is deferred pending consideration and disposition of a related issue in People v. Gallardo, S231260 (see Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.512(d)(2) ), or pending further order of the court. Submission of additional briefing, pursuant to California Rules of Court, rule 8.520, is deferred pending further order of the court. Defendant's petition for review is denied.
